author: Reuters
title: Blanchett honored with BFI Fellowship
text: London Academy Award-winning actress Cate Blanchett has added another honor to her list of accolades -- the British Film Institute's Fellowship. Blanchett was given the award on Saturday, the highest the BFI can bestow, for her outstanding contribution to film. She earlier attended the premiere of her latest film "Truth" at the London Film Festival.
